item.title: Riding the Light
item.description:
Riding the Light

Take a soaring journey across Austin, the Live Music Capital of the World. Shot in the winter of 2014-2013, "Riding the Light" presents the Austin skyline as you've never seen it before. I'm excited and proud to share this short film, my third solo hyperlapse cityscape project.

item.title: Austin City Limits Celebrates 40 Years "Not Fade Away"
item.description:
Austin City Limits Celebrates 40 Years "Not Fade Away"
